# AI Services Guidance

- Keep prompt builders deterministic and domain-specific to handoff deliverables.
- Require structured outputs (JSON schema-like shape) and reject malformed model responses.
- Separate prompt construction, model call, parsing, and normalization into testable units.
- Treat model output as untrusted input; sanitize and validate before persistence.
- Include enough metadata to support HITL review and later audit reconstruction.
